Titolo: Death and Taxes (video game)

Anno: 2020

Descrizione: Death and Taxes is a simulation video game by Leene KÃ¼nnap, an Estonian indie game developer, and published through their company, Placeholder Gameworks on February 20, 2020. The game has the player take the role of a Grim Reaper, who must bureaucratically decide the fates of humans, specifically whether they will live or die. The game shares its ideology with the Death-Positive movement. On March 18, 2020, Placeholder Gameworks uploaded the game code under the MIT License on GitHub.



Genere: Puzzle 

Valutazione: N/A
